==制作==
影片剧本由奥斯汀·本恩和导演约翰·克洛基达斯共同基于真实事件创作，这也是克洛基达斯首次导演长片。<ref name=5Qs/>2008年，二人完成剧本后找到当时正与本恩合作著书的制作人{{link-en|克里斯婷·瓦陈|Christine Vachon}}，三人于是展开合作开始了电影的制作。<ref name=5Qs>{{cite web|url=http://filmmakermagazine.com/62863-five-questions-with-kill-your-darlings-director-john-krokidas/|title=Five Questions with Kill Your Darlings Director John Krokidas|work=Filmmaker|date=2013-01-18|accessdate=2014-07-16|archive-date=2021-01-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126014323/https://filmmakermagazine.com/62863-five-questions-with-kill-your-darlings-director-john-krokidas/|dead-url=no}}</ref>选角期间，[[丹尼尔·拉德克利夫|丹尼尔·拉德克利夫]]正在[[百老匯劇院|百老汇]]出演戏剧《[[恋马狂_(戏剧)|-{zh-cn:恋马狂;zh-tw:馬;}-]]》，他参与了试镜并获得艾伦·金斯堡一角。然而拍摄由于资金不足而迟迟未能开始，丹尼尔于是重回《[[哈利·波特|哈利·波特]]》剧组拍摄《哈利·波特与死亡圣器》的[[哈利·波特与死亡圣器（上）|上]]、[[哈利·波特与死亡圣器（下）|下]]两部。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.getsurrey.co.uk/whats-on/film-news/daniel-radcliffe-latest-role-allen-6422475|title=Daniel Radcliffe on his latest role and life after Harry Potter|work=Get Surrey|date=2013-12-18|accessdate=2014-07-16|archive-date=2019-06-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190629145612/https://www.getsurrey.co.uk/whats-on/film-news/daniel-radcliffe-latest-role-allen-6422475|dead-url=no}}</ref>在此期间，[[克里斯·埃文斯|克里斯·埃文斯]]、[[杰西·艾森伯格|杰西·艾森伯格]]和[[本·威士肖|本·威士肖]]等人也参与了试镜。随后电影在{{link-en|迈克尔·本纳罗亚|Michael Benaroya}}的帮助下获得足够资金，于2012年正式开始拍摄，导演克洛基达斯决定仍由丹尼尔饰演艾伦·金斯堡一角。<ref name=5Qs/><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/daniel-radcliffe-cast-allen-ginsberg-kill-your-darlings-284292|title=Daniel Radcliffe Officially Lands Role as Poet Allen Ginsberg|work=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]]|date=2012-01-24|accessdate=2014-07-16|archive-date=2020-08-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200804232132/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/daniel-radcliffe-cast-allen-ginsberg-kill-your-darlings-284292|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/movies/news/a361902/daniel-radcliffe-signed-for-allen-ginsberg-role-says-casting-director.html|title=Daniel Radcliffe signed for Allen Ginsberg role, says casting director|date=2012-01-24|work=[[Digital_Spy|Digital Spy]]|accessdate=2014-07-16|archive-date=2015-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924081257/http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/movies/news/a361902/daniel-radcliffe-signed-for-allen-ginsberg-role-says-casting-director.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>电影在哥伦比亚大学和纽约市周边取景，只用了24天便完成了拍摄。<ref name=5Qs/>

==反响与评价==
《杀死汝爱》获得了评论界总体正面的评价。媒体评论网站[[烂番茄|烂番茄]]综合了125位评论家的评价，其中76%的评论家给出正面评价，平均给分为6.6分（满分10分）。网站给出的评语中称：“影片凭借着丹尼尔·拉德克利夫和戴恩·德哈恩之间强烈的化学反应，把‘[[垮掉的一代|垮掉的一代]]’早期的故事推到了聚光灯的焦点上。”<ref name="Rotten Tomatoes">{{cite web|url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/kill_your_darlings_2013/|title=Kill Your Darlings (2013)|publisher=[[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]]|accessdate=2014-07-16|archive-date=2014-07-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140710231946/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/kill_your_darlings_2013/|dead-url=no}}</ref>另一家评论网站[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]根据36位评论家的影评，给影片打出65分（满分100分）的分数，以及“总体好评”的评语。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/kill-your-darlings |title=Kill Your Darlings |publisher=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]] |accessdate=2014-07-16 |archive-date=2014-04-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140401235518/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/kill-your-darlings |dead-url=no }}</ref>

《[[每日电讯报|每日电讯报]]》评论家罗比·柯林（{{lang|en|Robbie Collin}}）给影片打出了三星（满分五星）的评价，称这部影片“探讨了这场文学运动的价值，如实表现了这些角色的天赋才能。”<ref name="The Telegraph">{{cite web |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/film/filmreviews/10288843/Kill-Your-Darlings-review.html |title=Kill Your Darlings, Venice Film Festival, review |first=Robbie |last=Collin |date=2013-09-05 |work=[[The_Daily_Telegraph|The Daily Telegraph]] |location=London |accessdate=2014-07-16 |archive-date=2014-04-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140428152319/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/film/filmreviews/10288843/Kill-Your-Darlings-review.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>同一媒体的另一评论家詹妮·麦卡特尼（{{lang|en|Jenny McCartney}}）更是称赞影片是“会动的诗歌”。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/film/filmreviews/10500915/Kill-Your-Darlings-Poetry-in-motion.html|title=Kill Your Darlings: Poetry in motion|date=2013-09-05|work=[[The_Daily_Telegraph|The Daily Telegraph]]|first=Jenny|last=McCartney|location=London|accessdate=2014-07-16|archive-date=2017-06-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170626222553/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/film/filmreviews/10500915/Kill-Your-Darlings-Poetry-in-motion.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>《[[卫报|卫报]]》评论家达蒙·怀斯（{{lang|en|Damon Wise}}）看过影片在圣丹斯电影节的首映之后给影片打出四星（满分五星）的分数，盛赞影片“真材实料”，是“探索美国20世纪文学中真实的反传统文化开端的一次真正尝试”。他还称影片“创造了真实的能量感和激情感…… 讲述了一个理智和道德的艰难抉择，在当时已经是一个完美的故事，在今天仍然与观众产生共鸣。”<ref>{{cite news |last=Wise |first=Damon |title=Sundance film festival 2013: Kill Your Darlings - first look review |url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/film/2013/jan/20/sundance-film-festival-review-kill-your-darlings |work=[[The_Guardian|The Guardian]] |location=London |date=2013-01-20 |accessdate=2014-07-16 |archive-date=2013-07-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130724190321/http://www.guardian.co.uk/film/2013/jan/20/sundance-film-festival-review-kill-your-darlings |dead-url=no }}</ref>《[[综艺_(杂志)|综艺]]》杂志评论家贾斯汀·张（{{lang|en|Justin Chang}}）评价影片“以出色的表演技巧、黑暗的诗歌意象和1940年代的生动场景，重现了垮掉一代的神秘注解。”<ref>{{cite news |last=Chang |first=Justin |title=Review: 'Kill Your Darlings' |url=http://www.variety.com/review/VE1117949009/ |work=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]] |date=2013-01-18 |accessdate=2014-07-16 |archive-date=2013-02-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130202044145/http://www.variety.com/review/VE1117949009/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>影评人对片中演员的演技也给出了好评。《[[独立报|独立报]]》影评人艾玛·琼斯（{{lang|en|Emma Jones}}）称赞丹尼尔·拉德克利夫有“决定性的演技”，称他“和18岁的金斯堡一样出色”。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/films/reviews/sundance-film-festival-review-kill-your-darlings--daniel-radcliffe-provides-a-defining-performance-as-beat-poet-allen-ginsberg-8458473.html|title=Sundance Film Festival review: Kill Your Darlings - Daniel Radcliffe provides a defining performance as Beat poet Allen Ginsberg|date=2013-01-19|accessdate=2014-07-18|work=[[The_Independent|The Independent]]|first=Emma|last=Jones|archive-date=2015-07-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150723004010/http://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/films/reviews/sundance-film-festival-review-kill-your-darlings--daniel-radcliffe-provides-a-defining-performance-as-beat-poet-allen-ginsberg-8458473.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>
丹尼尔·拉德克里夫在片中出演的同性床戏也获得大量关注。他在主演了《[[哈利·波特|哈利·波特]]》系列电影之后曾正面全裸出演戏剧《[[馬_(戲劇)|-{zh-cn:恋马狂;zh-tw:馬;}-]]》，这一次出演同性床戏也被认为是他的又一次突破。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.eonline.com/news/468084/daniel-radcliffe-says-gay-love-scenes-in-kill-your-darlings-are-tame-in-comparison-to-equus|title=Daniel Radcliffe Says Gay Love Scenes in Kill Your Darlings Are "Tame" in Comparison to Equus|work=[[Entertainment_Weekly|Entertainment Weekly]]|date=2013-10-08|last=Toomey|first=Alyssa|accessdate=2014-07-25|archive-date=2015-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924084901/http://www.eonline.com/news/468084/daniel-radcliffe-says-gay-love-scenes-in-kill-your-darlings-are-tame-in-comparison-to-equus|dead-url=no}}</ref>《[[娱乐周刊|娱乐周刊]]》编辑杰夫·拉布莱克（{{lang|en|Jeff Labrecque}}）还称赞戴恩·德哈恩在片中的演技堪称“明星级别”。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://insidemovies.ew.com/2013/10/01/daniel-radcliffe-in-kill-your-darlings-dane-dehaan-is-the-man-exclusive-video/|title=Daniel Radcliffe in 'Kill Your Darlings': 'Dane DeHaan is the man'|work=[[Entertainment_Weekly|Entertainment Weekly]]|date=2013-10-01|accessdate=2014-07-18|first=Jeff|last=Labrecque|archive-date=2014-07-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140725094722/http://insidemovies.ew.com/2013/10/01/daniel-radcliffe-in-kill-your-darlings-dane-dehaan-is-the-man-exclusive-video/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

部分评论家也给影片提出负面评价。影评网站{{link-en|The Dissolve|The Dissolve}}评论家萨姆·亚当斯（{{lang|en|Sam Adams}}）认为丹尼尔·拉德克利夫和戴恩·德哈恩两人的演技虽好，但影片“不懂得怎样好好利用他们的演技”，批评影片的拍摄手法“没有道理”。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://thedissolve.com/reviews/293-kill-your-darlings/|work=The Dissolve|date=2013-10-16|title=Kill Your Darlings|first=Sam|last=Adams|accessdate=2014-07-18|archive-date=2020-10-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201028144143/https://thedissolve.com/reviews/293-kill-your-darlings/|dead-url=no}}</ref>《[[洛杉矶时报|洛杉矶时报]]》影评人贝茨·夏奇（{{lang|en|Betsy Sharkey}}）则认为影片“过于保守”，并没有满足观众的预期。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/movies/moviesnow/la-et-kill-your-darlings-review-20131016-story.html|work=[[Los_Angeles_Times|Los Angeles Times]]|title=Review: Death and the Beats' birth drive 'Kill Your Darlings'|date=2013-10-16|accessdate=2014-07-18|first=Betsy|last=Sharkey|archive-date=2014-08-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140810034557/http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/movies/moviesnow/la-et-kill-your-darlings-review-20131016-story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

